# Syscall contract capture placeholder.
# Modules with volatile transitions can be filtered via validate_syscall_contract.py
# Use --module shim-ui to focus on UI-only syscalls or --module shim-game to limit to game module.
# For pointer-heavy transitions from shim-ui scoreboard updates, override arguments with --wildcard shim-ui:5,6.
# Example entries (origin module arg0 arg1 ...):
# vm-interpreted shim-ui 0000002A 00000000
# shim-ui shim-native 0000002A 00000000 00000001
